#. <section class="sutta" id="sn48.66"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn48.66:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.66:0.2"
msgid "7. Bodhipakkhiyavagga"
msgstr "7. Leading to Awakening"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 66. Dutiyaphalasutta → sattānisaṃsā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn48.66:0.3"
msgid "66. Dutiyaphalasutta"
msgstr "66. Seven Benefits"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.237"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.66:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, indriyāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five faculties."

msgctxt "sn48.66:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "sn48.66:1.3"
msgid "Saddhindriyaṃ … pe … paññindriyaṃ—"
msgstr "The faculties of faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom."

msgctxt "sn48.66:1.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañcindriyāni."
msgstr "These are the five faculties."

msgctxt "sn48.66:1.5"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā satta "
"phalā sattānisaṃsā pāṭikaṅkhā."
msgstr ""
"Because of developing and cultivating these five faculties, seven fruits and "
"benefits can be expected."

msgctxt "sn48.66:1.6"
msgid "Katame satta phalā sattānisaṃsā?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "sn48.66:1.7"
msgid "Diṭṭheva dhamme paṭikacca aññaṃ ārādheti, "
msgstr "They attain enlightenment early on in this very life. "

msgctxt "sn48.66:1.8"
msgid ""
"no ce diṭṭheva dhamme paṭikacca aññaṃ ārādheti, atha maraṇakāle aññaṃ "
"ārādheti."
msgstr "If not, they attain enlightenment at the time of death."

msgctxt "sn48.66:1.9"
msgid ""
"No ce diṭṭheva dhamme aññaṃ ārādheti, no ce maraṇakāle aññaṃ ārādheti, atha "
"pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā antarāparinibbāyī hoti, "
msgstr ""
"If not, with the ending of the five lower fetters, they’re extinguished in-"
"between one life and the next … "

msgctxt "sn48.66:1.10"
msgid "upahaccaparinibbāyī hoti, "
msgstr "they’re extinguished upon landing … "

msgctxt "sn48.66:1.11"
msgid "asaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti, "
msgstr "they’re extinguished without extra effort … "

msgctxt "sn48.66:1.12"
msgid "sasaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti, "
msgstr "they’re extinguished with extra effort … "

msgctxt "sn48.66:1.13"
msgid "uddhaṃsoto hoti akaniṭṭhagāmī."
msgstr "they head upstream, going to the Akaniṭṭha realm."

msgctxt "sn48.66:1.14"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā ime "
"satta phalā sattānisaṃsā pāṭikaṅkhā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Because of developing and cultivating these five faculties, these seven "
"fruits and benefits can be expected.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.66:1.15"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
